{"tid":620341,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭地鐵條女好似對我有意思","createTime":"2018-04-07T13:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T02:42:12.000Z","uid":119688,"like":35,"dislike":362,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"176f88b5a053f031ab71652e969b7654b4faa313","tid":620341,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"我係油麻地上車<br />\n一入去就見到有條女幾得幾正<br />\n咁作為男人對眼就緊係望靚女啦<br />\n點知望望下條女又望下我<br />\n打左幾下眼色,之後佢突然拉低左件褸條拉鍊 成條溝線好似紅海咁分開幾深,估唔到咁大波 我都扯扯地<br />\n但我好毒唔識溝,而且就到位<br />\n條女到底咩意思呢<br />\n<br />\n如果你見到呢個post pm我<br />\n想同你做愛 砌爆你"},{"pid":"f74abda151391b9b565cf73c82d0f2877164f768","tid":620341,"uid":47268,"like":441,"dislike":5,"score":436,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"小妹平時喺地鐵撚開唔少毒撚<br />\n原來今日嗰個你黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65252cf60b004cd5ae88bff27a828d84ea5c332","tid":620341,"uid":176011,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"柒頭衝上去屌啦，仲係度開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67239519ce8f90275568b77e794e3da53a1ded3","tid":620341,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  笑你無jerjer?"},{"pid":"10e2204632a6db4cfe0fbcf8409f79e54232c5df","tid":620341,"uid":35815,"like":96,"dislike":3,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"223867ca7b5b4da3d1bd1df2ec1344ef4cbe474e","tid":620341,"uid":5700,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"椰汁炸豬扒！椰汁炸豬扒！"},{"pid":"1db2fb79125f1f8e393e347eb784274bdc1a429a","tid":620341,"uid":24641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"椰汁炸豬扒 椰汁炸豬扒"},{"pid":"e50565526c1f0780ec9df013ad8e381b3b0f26e7","tid":620341,"uid":1